CRSITracker Notice

CRSITracker is developed based on the open-source CFTracker codebase, which itself is built upon CenterTrack and related third-party open-source components. The CFTracker-specific tracking modules and framework components have been removed or replaced by the proposed CRSITracker modules, while parts of the training, testing, data-processing, model-backbone, evaluation, and utility code may still be adapted from upstream projects.

